3 questions we often get asked when it comes to using “Castor Oil for Hair Growth” are:
 
1. WHO can use it? 🧐
2. HOW do I apply it? 🤔
3. WHEN do I wash it out?🤨
 
🥰We are here to help!🥰
 
Who can use it?
 
EVERYONE!  👩🏾👨🏻‍🦳🧒🏽👧🏻👩🏼‍🦱👩🏿‍🦲👩🏻‍🦲🧔🏽🧕🏼👩🏻‍🦱🧑🏾‍🦱🧑🏻‍🦰🧑🏽‍🦳👱🏻‍♂️
Castor is great on ALL hair types and textures! The application may vary depending on thickness and how often you wash your hair.
 
How do I apply it?
 
Step 1: Start off by parting and sectioning your hair with a hair clip. The thicker your hair, the more sections needed.✔️
 
Step 2: Apply a few drops to your scalp and roots, running it along the full length of the hairline.✔️
 
Step 3: Using your fingers, gently massage💆🏾‍♀️your scalp to spread the oil, making sure your entire scalp is loved.✔️
 
Step 4: Lock in the moisture 💦 with a hair covering or shower cap (preferably🌘overnight). For optimal results wrap a hot towel over the shower cap -  the heat🔥 encourages the hair follicles to open and really allow the oil to penetrate into your scalp.✔️
 
Step 5: Add a few drops of castor oil to your shampoo🧴 and conditioner before rinsing 🚿 thoroughly.✔️
 
When do I wash it out?
 
It’s your preference! Whether you wash your hair every day or once per month, it doesn’t 🤷🏾‍♂️ matter! 

🌟For the best results please practice patience and consistency: Apply 2/3 times per week for a few months🌟

Basic Rules:
1️⃣1️⃣There are 28 dominoes, each player draws seven.
 
2️⃣2️⃣The player with the highest same number domino “Double Six 6️⃣6️⃣” goes first.
 
3️⃣3️⃣If you don’t have a domino that corresponds to the ones on the board, you must pass. (Emphatically or otherwise)
 
4️⃣4️⃣The first person to run out of dominoes wins

5️⃣5️⃣If the game is blocked (everybody passes), the winner is the person with the lowest domino score (number of dots).

When do I wash it out?
 
It’s your preference! Whether you wash your hair every day or once per month, it doesn’t 🤷🏾‍♂️ matter!
